---
import Layout from "@/components/base/Layout.astro";
import { BUSINESS } from "@/utils/constants";
---

<Layout seo={{ title: "Privacy Policy", noindex: true }}>
  <section class="pt-28 pb-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-cosmic">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-brand-grey mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you submit our contact form, we collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Your name (first and last)</li>
        <li>Your email address</li>
        <li>The nature of your inquiry</li>
        <li>Any message content you provide</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not collect sensitive health information through this website. Any health information you choose to share through our contact form is provided voluntarily.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information you provide solely to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Respond to your inquiry</li>
        <li>Schedule consultations or appointments</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about our services</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We never sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
      <p>Contact form submissions are transmitted via secure, encrypted connections (HTTPS). Form data is stored only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry and is then deleted. We do not maintain a database of client information through this website.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
      <p>This website does not use cookies, analytics trackers, or advertising pixels. We do not track your browsing behavior.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Our contact form is processed by Web3Forms, a third-party form handling service. Their privacy policy is available at web3forms.com. Aside from this, no third-party services collect data through our website.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request that we delete any personal information you have submitted through our contact form. To make such a request, email us at {BUSINESS.email}.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about this privacy policy, contact:</p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        {BUSINESS.name}<br />
        {BUSINESS.location}<br />
        <a href={`mailto:${BUSINESS.email}`} class="text-brand-teal hover:underline">{BUSINESS.email}</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
